    • Constructor Detail

      • CBuildFromTableReader

        public CBuildFromTableReader(org.omancode.rmt.tablereader.AbstractTableReader tblreader,
                     String primaryKeys)
                      throws IOException
        Create table builder. Container name is the table name and will read column header from the table and load all columns using the default cell readers.
        Parameters:
        tblreader - table reader
        primaryKeys - column names of primary keys, separated by comma, eg: "firstname,lastname" NB: do not include a space after the comma.
        Throws:
        IOException - if IO problem reading table header.

      • CBuildFromTableReader

        public CBuildFromTableReader(org.omancode.rmt.tablereader.AbstractTableReader tblreader,
                     String containerName,
                     String[] primaryKeys)
                      throws IOException
        Construct a casper table builder.
        Parameters:
        tblreader - table reader
        containerName - if null will use default (the table name)
        primaryKeys - those keys that can be used as lookup keys in the returned casper dataset
        Throws:
        IOException - if IO problem reading table header.
